venv/

# Editor / scratch
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
scratch/

# Local agent state (Claude Code per-user settings/state — never shared)
.claude/

# Scraped source material (firecrawl skill cache — regenerable, goes stale; cite figures in ADRs/PLAN instead)
.firecrawl/
